StorageRoom,is,a,cloud,based,CMS,for,the,data,in,user,Mobile,Applications,It,provides,a,platform,to,manage,content,online,and,to,integrate,that,content,into,one,or,multiple,mobile,or,desktop,apps,The,API,lets,users,integrate,the,StorageRoom,service,into,their,applications,The,API,provides,almost,all,of,StorageRoom,s,functionality,including,Create,a,new,Collection,that,contains,further,Entries,Add,new,Entries,your,Collection,s,validation,rules,will,be,obeyed,Update,or,delete,any,Entry,Search,all,your,Entries,to,only,get,the,data,you,require,It,uses,RESTful,calls,and,responses,are,formatted,in,JSON